data.description: Come see this 5 bedroom 3 bath home located on the cul-de-sac in the popular Stonewall Farms neighborhood.  The ''Leighton'' floor plan offers an open floorplan with 2 bedrooms on the main floor and 2 bedrooms and a bonus room upstairs.  There is a private screened porch on the back which overlooks the lush, fenced backyard. Master suite features a vaulted ceiling, modern recessed lighting, a gorgeous bathroom with a stand up tiled showed, granite counters, a jetted tub, and a large walk-in closet. The 2nd bedroom on the main floor would make a great office, nursery or guest bedroom as it's next to a private full bath. The kitchen is open and features a beautiful island which overlooks the 2 story great room. The bedrooms on the 2nd floor are generous and have large closets.  The bonus room is HUGE and could be a 5th bedroom.
